==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tungsten steel
<hw>Tungsten steel</hw>. <fld>(Metal.)</fld> <def>A steel containing a
small amount of tungsten, noted for tenacity and hardness, even under a
considerable degree of heat. Magnets made of it are said to be highly
permanent. It often contains manganese.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tungstic</ent>⟦br⟧
